							<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-or shrink-0"></span> Lecture & Jeux</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-or shrink-0"></span> Promenades (avec ou sans chien)</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-or shrink-0"></span> Organisation évènement collectif</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card min-w-[85vw] md:min-w-0 snap-center bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-charbon/5 h-full flex flex-col group hover:border-or/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2">
					<div class="h-72 overflow-hidden relative shrink-0">
						<img src="/card_quotidien.png" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:brightness-110 group-hover:contrast-110 sepia-[30%]" alt="Sérénité Quotidienne"/>
						<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-charbon/10 group-hover:bg-transparent transition-colors"></div>
					</div>
					<div class="p-10 flex-1 flex flex-col relative">
						<h4 class="font-serif text-3xl mb-4 text-charbon group-hover:text-or transition-colors duration-300">Sérénité Quotidienne</h4>
						<div class="w-12 h-px bg-charbon/10 mb-6 group-hover:w-full group-hover:bg-or/20 transition-all duration-700"></div>
						<p class="text-lg text-charbon/70 leading-relaxed mb-8 font-light flex-1">Préserver l'autonomie en douceur. Nous veillons au confort matériel du foyer pour ne garder que le meilleur du quotidien.</p>
						<ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-bold text-charbon/80 uppercase tracking-wide mt-auto">
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-or shrink-0"></span> Petites Courses</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-or shrink-0"></span> Organisation Pharmacie</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-or shrink-0"></span> Rangement léger</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card min-w-[85vw] md:min-w-0 snap-center bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-charbon/5 h-full flex flex-col group hover:border-or/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2">
					<div class="h-72 overflow-hidden relative shrink-0">
						<img src="/card_assistance.png" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-all duration-1000 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:brightness-110 group-hover:contrast-110 grayscale-[50%]" alt="Assistance Privée"/>
