						<p class="text-lg text-charbon/70 leading-relaxed mb-8 font-light flex-1">La tranquillité d'esprit absolue. Tri, rendez-vous ou classement : nous transformons la complexité administrative en simplicité.</p>
						<ul class="space-y-4 text-sm font-bold text-charbon/80 uppercase tracking-wide mt-auto">
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-or shrink-0"></span> Tri du courrier</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-or shrink-0"></span> Prise de rendez-vous</li>
							<li class="flex items-center gap-3"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rotate-45 bg-or shrink-0"></span> Organisation Administrative</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="service-card min-w-[85vw] md:min-w-0 snap-center bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-charbon/5 h-full flex flex-col group hover:border-or/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:-translate-y-2">
					<div class="h-72 overflow-hidden relative shrink-0">
