								<span class="text-5xl font-serif text-charbon">39,50€</span>
								<span class="text-sm text-charbon/40">/mois</span>
							</div>
							<p class="text-xs text-charbon/40 mb-8 font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Après crédit d'impôt</p>
							<div class="w-full h-px bg-charbon/10 mb-8 group-hover:bg-or/30 transition-colors"></div>
							<ul class="space-y-4 text-base text-charbon/80 leading-relaxed flex-1">
								<li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-or mt-1 font-bold">◆</span> <span><strong>2 Visites de Convivialité</strong> (Café, jeux, discussion)</span></li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-or mt-1 font-bold">◆</span> <span><strong>Lien & Partage</strong> (Promenades quartier)</span></li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-or mt-1 font-bold">◆</span> <span><strong>Connexion Familiale</strong> (Aide WhatsApp/Visio)</span></li>
