							</ul>
						</div>

						<div class="plan-card relative bg-[#F9F7F2] text-charbon p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-charbon/5 hover:border-or/30 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-sm group overflow-hidden flex flex-col h-full" data-plan="Formule Confort">
							<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-or text-charbon text-[10px] font-bold px-5 py-2 rounded-bl-[1.5rem] uppercase tracking-widest z-20">Recommandée</div>
							<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
								<h4 class="font-serif font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-2xl text-stone-800 mb-4 group-hover:text-or transition-colors">Formule Confort</h4>
								<div class="min-h-[60px] mb-6"><p class="text-lg text-charbon/60 font-light italic">"Sérénité absolue & Gestion complète du quotidien."</p></div>
								<div class="flex items-baseline gap-4 mb-2">
									<span class="text-2xl text-charbon/30 line-through decoration-or decoration-1">159€</span>
									<span class="text-5xl font-serif text-charbon">79,50€</span>
									<span class="text-sm text-charbon/40">/mois</span>
								</div>
								<p class="text-xs text-charbon/40 mb-8 font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Après crédit d'impôt</p>
