									<li class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-or/5 rounded-lg border border-or/20"><span class="text-or mt-1 font-bold">★</span> <span><strong>Option Sécurité Incluse :</strong> Levée de doute & Déplacement rapide si inquiétude.</span></li>
								</ul>
							</div>
						</div>

						<div class="bg-charbon border border-white/10 rounded-[2.5rem] p-10 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-center h-full shadow-2xl">
							<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://grainy-gradients.vercel.app/noise.svg')] opacity-5 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
							<div class="relative z-10">
								<span class="inline-block py-1 px-4 border border-or/40 rounded-full text-[10px] font-sans tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-or mb-6 font-bold bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm">Dispositif d'État</span>
